The meaning of education means learning and expanding the learning of oneself, regardless of your age, ethinicity, gender, cutlure or even the society or country you are from. In the past, people tend to view education as a waste of time or just a kind of 'hobby' for the rich to do in order to past their time. The poor, on the other hand, had to work in order to sustain a living, needless to say the opportunity to gain knowledge. Nowadays, everyone has the right to go to Universities, doing their degrees, or even masters. In view of this, we can see a lof of people graduatinfg every year. Going to Uiversity is no longer a nolvety but in turn it is considered as a trend everywhere.